### logistics-agent 测试请求
### 前置：1) 启动 logistics-mcp-server (8080)  2) 设置 DASHSCOPE_API_KEY 并启动 logistics-agent (8081)
### 用法：安装 VS Code "REST Client" 扩展，点击各请求上方的 "Send Request"

@host = http://localhost:8081

### 1) 成功：用户 1001 + 运单 9001 → 创建工单成功，返回工单号
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-1001",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "用户1001的运单9001破损了，帮我创建一个客服工单，内容是包裹外箱破损"
}

### 2) 业务失败：运单 9999 不存在 → 解释并引导核对，不重试
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-1001",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "用户1001的运单9999要投诉，帮我建工单"
}

### 3) 系统失败（查询用户）：用户 1500 上游不可用 → "系统繁忙，请稍后重试"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-1500",
  "userId": 1500,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "用户1500的运单9001有问题，帮我建工单"
}

### 4) 系统失败（创建工单）：用户 1002 工单服务故障 → "系统繁忙，请稍后重试"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-1002",
  "userId": 1002,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "用户1002的运单9002延误，帮我建工单"
}

### 5) 纯查询：查运单状态（不创建工单）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-1001",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "帮我查一下用户1001的运单9001现在到哪了"
}

### ============================================================
### 查件（trackShipment）测试用例
### 工具只需运单 ID，无需用户身份验证
### ============================================================

### T1) 查件成功：运单 9001（IN_TRANSIT，北京→上海）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-track-9001",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "帮我查一下运单9001现在到哪了"
}

### T2) 查件成功：运单 9003（PENDING_PICKUP，上海→杭州）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-track-9003",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "运单9003的物流进度怎么样了？"
}

### T3) 查件成功：运单 9005（OUT_FOR_DELIVERY，深圳→广州）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-track-9005",
  "userId": 1002,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "我的运单9005现在到哪了？"
}

### T4) 查件成功：运单 9006（EXCEPTION，成都→重庆）
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-track-9006",
  "userId": 1002,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "能帮我查一下运单9006的状态吗？"
}

### T5) 查件业务失败：运单 9999 不存在 → 解释并引导核对，不重试
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-track-9999",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "帮我查一下运单9999到哪了"
}

### ============================================================
### 催件（expediteShipment）测试用例
### 工具需要用户 ID + 运单 ID + 催件原因
### 允许催件的状态：待取件、运输中、派送中、异常件
### ============================================================

### E1) 催件成功：用户 1001 + 运单 9001（IN_TRANSIT）→ 创建催件工单
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9001",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "运单9001太慢了，帮我加急一下"
}

### E2) 催件成功：用户 1001 + 运单 9003（PENDING_PICKUP）→ 创建催件工单
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9003",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "我的运单9003还没取件，我要催一下"
}

### E3) 催件成功：用户 1003 + 运单 9005（OUT_FOR_DELIVERY）→ 创建催件工单
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9005",
  "userId": 1003,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "运单9005派送太慢了，能加急处理吗"
}

### E4) 催件成功：用户 1003 + 运单 9006（EXCEPTION）→ 创建催件工单
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9006",
  "userId": 1003,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "运单9006变成异常件了，我要加急处理"
}

### E5) 催件业务失败：用户 1001 + 运单 9999 不存在 → 解释并引导核对
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9999",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "帮我催一下运单9999"
}

### E6) 催件业务失败：用户 1003 + 运单 9002（DELIVERED 已签收）→ 状态不支持催件
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9002",
  "userId": 1003,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "运单9002我要加急"
}

### E7) 催件业务失败：用户 1001 + 运单 9004（RETURNED 已退回）→ 状态不支持催件
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-9004",
  "userId": 1001,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "帮我催一下运单9004"
}

### E8) 催件系统失败：用户 1500（用户服务超时）+ 运单 9001 → "系统繁忙，请稍后重试"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-1500",
  "userId": 1500,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "用户1500的运单9001太慢了，帮我加急"
}

### E9) 催件系统失败：用户 1002（工单服务不可用）+ 运单 9005 → "系统繁忙，请稍后重试"
POST {{host}}/api/v1/agent/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": "sess-expedite-1002-9005",
  "userId": 1002,
  "roles": "agent-user",
  "message": "用户1002的运单9005派送太慢，帮我加急处理"
}
